cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything.

This outstanding example of a 2013 Hyundai Elantra Limited PZEV is offered by CDJR Franklin. When you purchase a vehicle with the CARFAX Buyback Guarantee, you're getting what you paid for. The Hyundai Elantra Limited PZEV is economically and environmentally smart.

This Corolla is a Local Trade with Clean Carfax History and is nicely equipped with Power Moonroof, 6-Speaker AM/FM/CD/MP3 Audio System, along with Alloy Wheels, Cruise Control, and Fog Lamps, plus Power steering, Power Windows, and Remote Keyless Entry.
